survey1_question1_text: On a scale of "snoozing under a cozy blanket" to "sprinting from a herd of stampeding elephants," how stressful was your day? (1 = Totally chill to 10 = Call the fire department, my brain is on fire!)
survey1_question2_text: Looking into your crystal ball, how much stress do you predict for tomorrow? (1 = Calm like a monk to 10 = Consider me officially overwhelmed!)
survey1_question3_text: Did your miracle stress-shrinking method (art activities) help you feel like a calm, happy puppy, or was it more like trying to train a cat to do your taxes? (1 = Not helpful at all to 10 = I'm practically levitating with calmness) (Answer ONLY if you have done the art therapy!)
survey1_question4_text: When you skipped the method (not doing art activities) today, did managing stress feel more like “breezing through a sunny park” or “juggling flaming torches while riding a unicycle on a tightrope over a pit of snapping crocodiles”? (1 = Easy breezy to 10 = Send help, I'm barely holding it together!) (Answer ONLY if the art activities have NOT been done!)
